data.description: Welcome home to this move-in-ready gem! Located in the highly desirable Joggers Run Community, this townhouse offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step into the heart of the home - the beautifully remodeled kitchen featuring custom backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and sleek white cabinetry. Cooking here will be an absolute delight! The bathrooms have also been given a modern makeover with newer vanities, toilets, and fixtures, plus custom bath fitter enclosures for that extra touch of luxury. You'll love the highly durable laminate wood flooring. The public schools are fantastic, and with Okeeheelee Park just around the corner, this property is a perfect fit for families who love outdoor activities. Schedule your private showing today!
